divs: Sighting DetailsI looked up at the clear night sky because I noticed movement, When I looked I seen a big star like object moving across the sky, I immediately got excited, and all of a sudden another star like object caused a bright flash or sparkle and disappeared. I looked for the other object and found it again moving at a more brisk pace and it gradually appeared to get smaller and disappear into the blackness of space. I stared up at the sky for a couple minutes after this and I noticed slow moving stars looking like they were moving on an orbit across the sky
